            {
                "comment": "For this capstone, we got to go on a lot of field trips to various sites around Madison which was really cool. There was no work outside of class until 2 weeks before the end of the semester she wanted 16 of us to write one 25 page paper. She is very picky at what she wants in it but doesn't give out guidelines or any direction with how to do it. ",
                "difficulty_rating": 3,
                "quality_rating": 1
