            {
                "comment": "The only way to do well in this class is to have super-human note taking abilities; everything is covered in lecture exclusively. No other learning materials are given to you(The text book is useless), and the slides are not posted, so you can't really improve your grade by working harder. Avoid this professor.",
                "difficulty_rating": 4,
